<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="black-adj">black <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /blæk/    美 /blæk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>黑色的；漆黑的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sky grew black with clouds. 
乌云密布，天色灰暗。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It was a cold and black night. 
那是一个寒冷、漆黑的夜晚。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>黑人的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>black culture 
黑人文化</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>(咖啡、茶) 不加奶油 / 牛奶的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I like my coffee black. 
我喜欢喝不加牛奶的咖啡。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="black-humour">black humour</h3>
<p>1.<strong>黑色幽默</strong>  </p></div>